quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,31,"Àyàfi ’Iblīs. Ó kọ̀ láti wà nínú àwọn olùforíkanlẹ̀-kíni náà."
  15,32,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “’Iblīs, kí ló dí ọ lọ́wọ́ láti wà nínú àwọn olùforíkanlẹ̀-kíni?”"
  15,33,"Ó wí pé: “Èmi kò níí forí kanlẹ̀ kí abara kan tí O ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ láti ara amọ̀ tó ń dún koko, tó ti pàwọ̀dà.”"
  16,10,"Òun ni Ẹni tó ń sọ omi kalẹ̀ láti sánmọ̀. Mímu wà fún yín nínú rẹ̀. Igi ewéko tún ń wù jáde láti inú rẹ̀, tí ẹ fi ń bọ́ àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn."
  16,11,"(Allāhu) tún ń fi (omi yìí) hu àwọn irúgbìn, igi òróró zaetūn, igi dàbínù, igi àjàrà àti gbogbo àwọn èso (yòókù) jáde fún yín. Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún ìjọ tó ní àròjinlẹ̀."
  16,12,"Ó rọ òru, ọ̀sán, òòrùn, òṣùpá àti àwọn ìràwọ̀ fún yín pẹ̀lú àṣẹ Rẹ̀. Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún ìjọ tó ní làákàyè."